{"about_the_game":"Flex your strategic mastery in <strong>Rogue Citadel</strong>, a fusion of <strong>tower defence</strong> and <strong>survivors</strong> gameplay set within the foreboding Castle Shadowfell. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/RogueCitadel_Combat01-smol.gif?t=1727376496\" /><br><br>Battle your way through the <strong>procedurally generated</strong> layers of the castle, adapting your defences to hold off waves of varied horrors.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/RogueCitadel_Crafting02-smol.gif?t=1727376496\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Survivors-style Gameplay</h2>Ancient and often bizarre heroes guide you through your adventure, granting you their unique and powerful abilities.<br><br>Build up your hero with carefully chosen upgrades and equipment, gaining in power between runs.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/RogueCitadel_Upgrade01-smol.gif?t=1727376496\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Deckbuilding Tower Defence</h2>Construct your deck of defences to keep you and your resources safe as you delve deeper into the Castle.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/RogueCitadel_Crafting01-smol.gif?t=1727376496\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Procedural Levels</h2>Every level has a unique layout where scouting and placement of your defences will be key.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/RogueCitadel_Base01-smol.gif?t=1727376496\" /><br><br>Play the demo now to check out an early version of the gameplay, and join our Discord channel to discuss your adventures!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Dungeon Lobby Normal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamc